# ============================================================
# SECTION U - UMBRELLA CLAIMS (M1.6 refactor — load-bearing set)
#
# Per substrate-convergence (mizaj 02 + 07 + atoms 0011 + 0015): the
# previous 27-claim plan invited compositional dilution of joint
# confidence. Most claims were derived or supporting, not independently
# load-bearing. Refactored: 5 umbrella claims that each have DIRECT
# evidence (not derived from sub-claim composition). The umbrellas
# enter the new discharge theorem; the existing detail claims stay as
# supporting evidence (Sections O/A/B/C/D/E/F/H/I/J above) but no
# longer enter the joint-confidence chain.
#
# Why 5 umbrellas escape compositional dilution: each has DIRECT
# evidence at its tier ceiling (L1 own, L3 mutawatir, L1+L2
# synthesized) - the umbrella's confidence is set by its evidence,
# not by the min of its sub-claims.
# ============================================================

