#
# HONESTY-VERIFICATION CORRECTION (atom 0015 + 0010):
# Claims about "actively maintained" and "weekly rebase cadence" for
# cpkt9762 were NOT supported by the repo's actual content — only the
# pattern documentation. So evidence is "the thin-fork pattern is
# documented as design intent" not "the pattern has been operationally
